There was a good day for Jim.
When he went out, the sun was shining and the birds were singing.
Then he got in his car.
Before work, he was stopped at a coffee shop.
He ordered a coffee and a sandwich.
Then he went to work.
There were an avarage workday.
Except he had a good conversation with his boss.
It is looks like Jim is going to get a promotion.
He is waiting for this promotion for years.
After work, he was told the good news to his friends.
And after that, he won some dollar on a scratch card.
He diceded, that he took his girlfriend to a restaurant at this day.
He was told the good news to his girlfriend too.
His girlfriend is happy too.
After they finished, they are went home.
There can not be perfect.
He scratched his car, when he went out from the parking lot.
He was a bit sad when they got home.
But then he remembered what happened in the office.
His girlfriend told him, there is not a thing, that Jim should be worried about.
After that, they both agree that they had a good day.
Jim was happy when he went to the bad.
He is thinking now, that his life is going on the right way.
After that, he is thinking about his decesions from the past.
But then he fall asleep.
